    2. December 11th, 1998, 06:52 AM [44]#2
       [45]olaf
          + [46]View Profile
          + [47]View Forum Posts
       olaf is offline Junior Member

        Join Date
                Dec 1998

        Location
                Spain

        Posts
                1

     If you have 2 IDE plugs in your I/O controller, the second one is
     only for ISA stuff, you could only put there your CR-ROM. You will
     put both Hd in the first plug, with a two-pin fat cable.
       [48]Reply With Quote Reply With Quote [49]Share on Google+
         ______________________________________________________________

